text: Sky Is Open is the sixth studio album by the American singer and songwriter Donna de Lory, independently released on July 19, 2006. Three songs on the album originally appeared on her fourth studio album In the Glow (2003): "One Day", "Glow" and "In the Sun". == Track listing == == References == Category:2006 albums Category:Donna De Lory albums
title: Sky Is Open (album)
